    <briefdescription>
<para>RTIO Predefined Priorities. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Priorities are optionally used by I/O devices when scheduling operations. These priorities may lead to software or hardware bus arbitrators.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Today these are mostly unused but you should specify them. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
